                                            },
                                            {
                                                "instruction":  {
                                                                    "type":  "prompt",
                                                                    "text":  "Apologise and offer to transfer. Say: \u0027I apologise, but I encountered an issue while trying to save your appointment. Let me transfer you to one of our team members who can complete this for you right away. Please hold for just a moment.\u0027"
