                                                "instruction":  {
                                                                    "type":  "prompt",
                                                                    "text":  "The caller said something unclear. Politely ask them to repeat. Say: \u0027I am sorry, I did not quite catch that. Could you please repeat? I can help you book an appointment, answer questions about our clinic, or connect you to our team.\u0027"
